OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA day of sunny spells and a few
OL,6,Fshowers. Most places will remain dry
OL,7,Fand showers will be lighter than
OL,8,Frecent days. Winds on the light side
OL,9,Fso feeling pleasant in the sunnier
OL,10,Fmoments.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloud will thicken through
OL,13,Fthe evening as a band of rain moves in
OL,14,Ffrom the south overnight. The rain may
OL,15,Fturn heavy towards dawn. Gusty winds
OL,16,Falso developing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
